    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265430/extras/feac26fdfab286401a474545dd791efa.poster.avif?t=1729180273\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265430/extras/feac26fdfab286401a474545dd791efa.webm?t=1729180273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>听说麸质食品有害健康？哈！准备好迎接极端致命的面团吧！受到老巫婆的诅咒，这面团注定要在地球上游荡，给村庄和城镇带来毁灭。所以，进攻吧！记住——每次失败只会让你变得更强。在欢快的背景音乐中，《Breadborn》将为你带来活力四射、混沌无序的战斗！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >来，把它们打得落花流水！</h2><br>您可以尝试面包屑大军的所有控制方式。吸收它们来壮大你的身体，让自己变得更加强大。或者把它们吐向敌人，让这些小捣蛋鬼把敌人撕成碎片。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我们揉捏出武器，很多很多武器！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265430/extras/dd0fa4c6542fda90e96c8eb99740ff97.poster.avif?t=1729180273\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265430/extras/dd0fa4c6542fda90e96c8eb99740ff97.webm?t=1729180273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在演示版中，您将评估并实践几种近战和远程武器，这些武器将在正式版中等待您。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >像面团一样发迹吧！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265430/extras/08d56fbc912baafe7d5f672502cee8a5.poster.avif?t=1729180273\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265430/extras/08d56fbc912baafe7d5f672502cee8a5.webm?t=1729180273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在教程关卡和两个充满危险敌人、升级和有趣任务的大型战斗地点中一路过关斩将。变得更强、更聪明、更大、更危险！",
